{"tid":1647290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家明吾明\"死因裁判官\"的職權範圍","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:37:51.000Z","uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29bbf118effcce32d613bc895cc5c851978911f7","tid":1647290,"uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"死因裁判官的職權範圍 <br />\n死因裁判官為司法人員，有權：<br />\n發出埋葬命令<br />\n發出火葬命令<br />\n批准免將屍體剖驗<br />\n<strong>發出屍體剖驗命令</strong><br />\n發出檢掘遺骸命令<br />\n發出命令將屍體運離香港<br />\n<strong>命令警方調查死亡個案</strong><br />\n<strong>命令進行研訊</strong><br />\n批准切除及使用其死者部份器官<br />\n簽發死亡事實證明書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/court_services_facilities/cor.html#6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fzh%2Fcourt_services_facilities%2Fcor.html%236&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=75e05c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.judiciary.hk/zh/court_services_facilities/cor.html#6</a>"},{"pid":"0f5a6c357c63810734329f1c429893481d1b3412","tid":1647290,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"墮樓＝生前比人打到骨折　浮屍＝生前比人強姦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589268</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8cc01a74530944ecba7744db8971fddd23faa810","tid":1647290,"uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"631ae37f6ccf2336a8c08752b80e1ab33d3e96d3","tid":1647290,"uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"39c108598698768e3e6959306bceabcda3792e68","tid":1647290,"uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"司法界係時候出馬"},{"pid":"99bd1cac9f091b36aaa26780d846645d9e803b99","tid":1647290,"uid":269022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:37:04.000